<p>Welcome. This post exists to show every building block you’ll reuse.</p>
<section id="math" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="math">Math</h2>
<p>Inline math like <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?e%5E%7Bi%5Cpi%7D%20+%201%20=%200"> works, and so do display equations:</p>
<p><span id="eq-gradient"><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%0A%5Cnabla_%5Ctheta%20%5C,%20%5Cmathcal%7BL%7D(%5Ctheta)%20=%20%5Cmathbb%7BE%7D_%7Bx%20%5Csim%20%5Cmathcal%7BD%7D%7D%5C!%5Cleft%5B%20%5Cnabla_%5Ctheta%20%5C,%20%5Cell(f_%5Ctheta(x),%20y)%20%5Cright%5D%0A%5Ctag%7B1%7D"></span></p>
<p>You can cross-reference it: see Equation&nbsp;1.</p>
</section>
