<section id="citing-arxiv-papers" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="citing-arxiv-papers">Citing arXiv papers</h2>
<p>Cite a paper inline like this <span class="citation" data-cites="vaswani2017attention">(Vaswani et al. 2017)</span> and the reference list is built automatically at the bottom from <code>references.bib</code>. To add a paper: open its arXiv page → “Export BibTeX citation” → paste the entry into <code>references.bib</code>.</p>
